<taxonomicName id="4C394D44CA1E5339FC14CF3F28510E3E" authorityName="Vorontsova &amp; Christenhusz &amp; Kirika &amp; Muthoka" authorityYear="2010" box="[915,1126,264,285]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="11" pageNumber="905" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="malindiense">Solanum malindiense</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
is named after the town of Malindi near the site of its first discovery.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
